[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/basic_major"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST has a normal opening bid of 1\S.

WEST has a Limit Raise in \Ss, 11 points and 4 \Ss. 
He responds 3\S

EAST figures that 15 points is enough for game with partner showing 11/12. 
She bids 4\S.}

