[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/basic_major"]
[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 6 points and wouldn't dream of opening.

SOUTH has 17 points, counting three extra length points, so she opens 1\H.

NORTH does have enough to raise to 2\H.

SOUTH makes one more try, inviting with a 3\H bid but NORTH just passes.}

